    {
        "client_msg_id": "4f9b1b83-e471-4c58-845f-15ec693b8c25",
        "type": "message",
        "text": "Overall, sure. For right now, let's pursue something practical, or keep making due here.\n\nBut since the topic of better collaboration tools (in general, not just for us here and now) has already been a topic before, maybe we should at least consider (even just as a thought exercise) what it would take, even just minimally, to roll our own?\n\nIf the answer is close in reach, then we get to consider something we'd not have considered otherwise. If it's not in reach for the short term, but worth pursuing at all, then maybe it becomes it's own side project that eventually takes us somewhere (e.g. better tools for bootstrapping the future)",
        "user": "UAVCC2X70",
